- Umetnost?

280
00:21:13,675 --> 00:21:17,133
- Oh, znaci ti si umetnica?
- Oh. Ne znam jos.

281
00:21:17,579 --> 00:21:18,568
To je bas divno.

282
00:21:19,915 --> 00:21:21,849
Dali pravis nesto ili?

283
00:21:23,452 --> 00:21:24,441
Ne znam jos.

284
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:27,617
Svejedno, srecno s time.

285
00:21:30,358 --> 00:21:31,655
Oh.

286
00:21:39,066 --> 00:21:40,624
Ti...

287
00:21:40,801 --> 00:21:44,964
